text: Kugarchi () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Surensky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 856 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Kugarchi
